                            </div>
<br><br>
                            <p style="padding: 0px 0px 3% 0px;font-size: 23px;color: black; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif,';">
                                Here are a few tips that would help you strike a balance between your personal and professional life:
                                <br>
                                1. Plan your Schedule in Advance

                                <br>
                                2. Designate ‘No-Work’ Slots

                                <br>
                                3. Take Out Time for Your Interests 

                                <br>
                                4. Recharge During Weekends 

                                <br>
                                5. Be Assertive (Learn to Say ‘No’)

                                <br>
                                6. Unplug from All Devices 

                                <br>
                                7. Connect with Family and Friends

                                <br>
                                8. Delegate Work 

                                <br>
                                9. Ascertain your Working Capacity 

                                <br>
                                10. TSeek Peer Support 

<br>
                            </p>
